data.description: Are you looking for that perfect blend of privacy yet still be close to all the modern amenities of the city? Look no further. You can't go wrong with this location. This beautiful mountain home is on 5 acres in Van Gilder Farm Subdivision. Master bed on main level, gas fireplace in the large open great room. Large bonus room, office and more bedrooms in the upper level. New carpet, paint, new covered rear porch, new concrete sidewalk and water treatment are just some of the upgrades. Enjoy the spacious kitchen and stainless steel appliances. Appreciate the privacy of the rear covered deck while drinking your coffee in the mornings. Watch  the deer and turkey travel by as you delight in your own piece of paradise. Located off Boyds Creek close to stores, restaurants, and more on Chapman Hwy and Winfield Dunn Pkwy; 30 minutes to Pigeon Forge and 25 minutes to Neyland Stadium. The backyard is a future haven awaiting the new owner's personal touch HOA covers entrance landscaping and lighting. Sellers are giving $1000.00 dollars with acceptable offer to use toward grass seed and straw.
